cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the application of neural networks for locating anatomical landmarks in 3D medical CT scans. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The use of Gaussian heatmaps and affine mapping also suggests the involvement of multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
